# Spotify "Now Playing" widget (optional, site works without it)
# 1. Create an app at https://developer.spotify.com/dashboard (redirect URI: http://127.0.0.1:3000/callback)
# 2. Get a refresh token with scopes: user-read-currently-playing user-read-recently-played user-top-read
#    (see README "Spotify integration" for the one-time auth steps)
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_ID=
SPOTIFY_CLIENT_SECRET=
SPOTIFY_REFRESH_TOKEN=
